        java.lang.Boolean checkUserCanRegisterInContest(java.lang.Integer userId,
                                                java.lang.Integer contestId)
                                         throws AppException
        Check whether some user can be register in one contest. If any team contains this user is accepted in the contest, this user can not register in this contest again.
        Parameters:
        userId - user's id.
        contestId - contest's id.
        Returns:
        true if user can register in specified contest.

        AppException
